# Pattern AI Assistant

Follow the specs in `.agents/`:

- **UI copy**: Brazilian Portuguese (`assets/js/i18n/pt-br.js`).
- **Code and comments**: English.
- **Layers**: `domain` → `application` → `infrastructure` / `presentation` (see `.agents/ARCHITECTURE.md`).
- **Patterns in code**: Strategy (AI providers), Adapters (HTTP), Facade (analysis flow) — see `.agents/PATTERNS-IN-CODE.md`.
- **ES modules**: serve over HTTP; `file://` may fail.

Do not add a bundler unless the user asks. Prefer small, focused modules and SOLID-friendly boundaries.
